What you need to compile :
	- OpenGL (with glut) => see http://www.mesa3d.org
	- glui => see http://www.cs.unc.edu/~rademach/glui

here are installation instructions :
	- edit Makefile to see if it fits to your config
	- edit src/config.h to see if it fits to your config
	- `make`
	- test with `test` or the various `bench-time-*`
	- copy (or not) the executable OpenGLavity whereever you want (typically /usr/local/bin or /opt/bin)